snippet.title: Johnny Depp Says He Feels Boycotted by Hollywood After 'Surreal' Years Following Amber Heard Split!
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp Says He Feels Boycotted by Hollywood After 'Surreal' Years Following Amber Heard Split!

Welcome back to Story Spot. For the channel today, we are going to feature the story about Johnny Depp Says He Feels Boycotted by Hollywood After 'Surreal' Years Following Amber Heard Split. In a recent interview, Johnny Deep revealed what is bothering him right now in his career.

The Pirates of the Caribbean actor said that he feels like he is being boycotted by Hollywood. This is after his recent movie Minamata is not given a U.S, release.
